                    </span>
                    <h3 class="fiu-card__heading">Hiring an apprentice</h3>
                    <p class="fiu-card__content">Apprenticeships help bring valuable skills into your organisation with the Government's support. Find out more about how this helps your organisation.</p>
                    <a href="/employers/hiring-an-apprentice" class="fiu-card__link fiu-card__link--employers">Learn more</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-quarter">
                <div class="fiu-card">
                    <span class="fiu-card__category">
                        <a class="fiu-card__category-link" asp-controller="LandingPage" asp-action="EmployersHowDoTheyWork">How do they work?</a>
                    </span>
                    <h3 class="fiu-card__heading">Upskilling your current staff</h3>
                    <p class="fiu-card__content">Apprenticeships are suitable for hiring new staff, but they're also ideal for upskilling or retraining your existing workforce. Either way, find out more here.</p>
                    <a href="/employers/upskill" class="fiu-card__link fiu-card__link--employers">Learn more</a>
                </div>
            </div>
