                    <h3 class="fiu-card__heading">Training your apprentice</h3>
                    <p class="fiu-card__content">During the apprenticeship, your apprentice will receive two different types of training. Find out what those types of training are, and more.</p>
                    <a href="/employers/training-your-apprentice" class="fiu-card__link fiu-card__link--employers">Learn more</a>
