                    <p class="fiu-card__content">Apprentices are assessed by an independent organisation to ensure they have the skills, knowledge and behaviours needed for their chosen occupation.</p>
                    <a href="/employers/end-point-assessments" class="fiu-card__link fiu-card__link--employers">Learn more</a>
                </div>
