                    <p class="fiu-card__content">Apprentices will spend at least 20% of their time on off-the-job training with your chosen training provider. Find out more about what this means.</p>
                    <a href="/employers/the-right-apprenticeship" class="fiu-card__link fiu-card__link--employers">Learn more</a>
                </div>
            </div>
